You are working on the frontend of The Bun Theory by Bakar & Roast.

Tech stack:
- NextJS (App Router)
- Typescript
- TailwindCSS
- shadcn/ui
- React Server Components

Rules:

1. Always use Typescript.
2. Use server components whenever possible.
3. UI must use shadcn components.
4. Avoid unnecessary client components.
5. Use TailwindCSS utility classes.
6. Components must be reusable.
7. API calls must be abstracted into /lib/api.
8. Images must use next/image.
9. Use optimistic UI for orders.

UX Rules:

- Mobile first design
- Big buttons for ordering
- Minimal form input
- Loading states required
- Use the project display font (Comic Sans fallback stack) for headings, titles, nav labels, labels, and CTA/button text.
- Keep body copy in the regular sans font unless the user requests otherwise.
